{
  "texts": [
    "The dimensions of these learned vectors are determined by the size of the weight matrices in the target layer.",
    "In this study, we inject an L q vector to scale the Q vector into the self-attention layer.",
    "Only the L q vector will be updated throughout the training process.",
    "The computation of the self-attention layer with (IA) 3 is described as follows:Attention(Q, K, V) = Softmax (L q Q)K T √ d V, (9)where represents element-wise multiplication.",
    "During the training process, the Q vector can be updated via elementwise multiplication with the L q vector."
  ]
}